  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It's a multicentric, randomized, controlled study concerning 100 patients with
      treatment-resistant obsessive compulsive disorders (OCD). The aim of this study is to
      evaluate the effect of transcranial direct current stimulation (tDCS) on OCD patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
